<br>
I'm looking for this self buff. <br>
<br>
Wrath of The Nameless<br>
<br>
Tar: Self Only<br>
Manna: 3000<br>
Cast time: .1<br>
Duration: 1 min<br>
Recast: .1<br>
<br>
HP           + 500 k<br>
Mana        + 40,000<br>
Regen(hp) + 10 k<br>
Regen(m)  + 500<br>
Resists     + 200 all<br>
Attack     + 6000<br>
Haste      + 3000<br>
Ac          + 5000 <br>
DS          + 450<br>
<br>
You are surrounded by a useful glow.<br>
SoAndSo feels a little bit tougher.<br>
<br>
And well these spells would help too:<br>
<br>
Karana's Judgement<br>
<br>
Manna:      3500<br>
Cast time:  1 seconds<br>
Damage:    25,000<br>
You throw your hands to the sky for ajudication.<br>
SoAndSo is struck by a bolt from the heavens.<br>
<br>
Wave of Clearing<br>
<br>
Manna:      4000<br>
Cast time:  2 seconds<br>
Damage:    25,000 (AoE)<br>
You throw your hands to the sky for ajudication.<br>
SoAndSo is struck by a bolt from the heavens.<br>
<br>
Druids Tractor<br>
Manna: 30,000<br>
Cast time: 9 ticks<br>
Effect: Zone (Reset)<br>
You flex at Everquest<br>
ZoneName is planted and seeded for being reset.<br>
<br>
I feel it would solve the &quot;Druid usefulness problem on raid.&quot;  I think it would eliminate the need for druids to join raids.<br>
<br>
Perhaps, some might see this as unbalencing.  Perhaps it is.  I suggest limiting it to level 60 &quot;Karana&quot; druids.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=26501.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=26501.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26501.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=26501.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.threadControl?topicID=26501.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26501.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26501.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT